def_cn: 呈递，提交，邮寄(参赛作品、求职信等)
def_en: If you send in something such as a competition entry or a letter applying for a job, you post it to the organization concerned.

def_cn: 派遣,调来(警察、军队等以应付危机或困难)
def_en: When a government sends in troops or police officers, it orders them to deal with a crisis or problem somewhere.
